{"tid":602363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣一地兩檢]在台就可「入境美國」可望成為亞太首例","createTime":"2018-03-23T03:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T04:37:27.000Z","uid":33890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f1652e254c3dc3669bcff0cd72cb25163e7954","tid":602363,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180323/1320419/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180323%2F1320419%2F&d=dXbaxH59gujBFwsrddcCrhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e052bfcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180323%2F1320419%2F&h=ce0ddf8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180323/1320419/</a><br />\n華航將於25日開航美國加州安大略，傳出華航與美方談判過程中，美方突破外交限制、初步敲定飛美航線擬將啟用「境外通關（US Border Preclearance）」措施，盼在台灣即可進行美國海關查驗，等同直接入境美國。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，華航董事長何煖軒表示，華航為拓展安大略航線與旅客便利，無心插柳，因安大略是國內機場，沒有海關與境外檢查中心，華航提議「在台灣桃園機場設海關」，美方相關單位立即接受。<br />\n<br />\n台灣101年11月正式加入美國免簽證計畫，去年11月再納入「全球入境計畫（Global Entry）」，讓台灣旅客可在美國快速通關。如今又可望在國內啟用「美國境外預先通關」，成為亞太第一個設置的國家。"},{"pid":"bbc5a14973b741a2e48b63e8ef7794025f6a1afe","tid":602363,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"大国(笑)口交部出嚟吠幾句啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ca3346dc327aa59c1bf7c17ce04872a4d903c","tid":602363,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"其實唔係咁正，加拿大嘈得好勁，因為改咗新制，個美國權限好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9628dd067b30ca82b5523ce452db3430ba009c5","tid":602363,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bbc5a14973b741a2e48b63e8ef7794025f6a1afe","tid":602363,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"大国(笑)口交部出嚟吠幾句啦<img